<title>USA: SystemSoft appoints new CFO.</title>
<headline>SystemSoft appoints new CFO.</headline>
<dateline>NATICK, Mass. 1997-07-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>SystemSoft Corp said on Thursday it appointed Paul Pedevillano chief financial officer, replacing David Sommers, who was leaving to pursue an entrepreneurial opportunity.</p>
<p>Pedevillano, who was SystemSoft's CFO from April 1993 to January 1996, was most recently senior vice president of operations at the company.</p>
<p>SystemSoft makes system-level software, connectivity and problem-resolution technologies.</p>
<p>The company also said William O'Connell and Jonathan Joseph were promoted to executive vice presidents.</p>
<p>((New York newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
